tweet: It's official. I hate making lesson plans, but I love teaching the lessons. So I guess it's worth it
#questionyouhate  Why waste your time? Well, because I don't think it's wasted time obviously!
Yesterday, I jumped in the leaves like a five-year-old. Today, I shook my booty like nobody's business. My name is Katie, and I'm impulsive.
I wish every day could be like this. Sleep in, no worries, do what you want. It should always be this easy. It should always be this simple.
Slept in until noon, still wearing my pj's!
